### TEST RESULTS

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test-results
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test-results/1
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test-results/patient/1
Accept: application/json

###

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/test-results
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "labTestId": 1,
  "doctorId": 1,
  "resultValue": "5.2",
  "unit": "mmol/L",
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-29"
}

###

